# GoMine Auth — 1 initData per line (1 per account)
# Get initData via Telethon or browser DevTools
#
# Format (single line, URL-encoded):
# query_id=AAHxxx...&user=%7B%22id%22%3A123456789%2C%22first_name%22%3A%22Test%22%7D&auth_date=1719000000&hash=abc123...
#
# Example (replace with your real initData):
query_id=AAHxxxEXAMPLE&user=%7B%22id%22%3A123456789%2C%22first_name%22%3A%22TestUser%22%7D&auth_date=1719000000&hash=example_hash_here
